long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Experience  your bowling skills in this addictive bowling  game! Try to hit all pins and score as many strikes as possible. dexterity is everything - wait for the right moment and click the power bar and angle indicator to throw the ball and knock all pins at the end of the lane over. Can you be the best?
